snippet.title: Updated Announcement Trailer [Portal BAGLEY]
snippet.description:
The first version of the trailer is still available here: https://youtu.be/kGWt9NDm6-c

The music is still made by our composer: @rolloutfr 

Feel free to join the Portal: BAGLEY Discord: https://discord.com/invite/reD4TM5W7X
As well as adding the game to your Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2420570/Portal_BAGLEY
And of course to support the project: https://fr.tipeee.com/portalbagley
